::KitKat::

She looked at Destructor. "No waiting. I know what I must do know.  
WE will crysh the Allince first.  The maximals have until we are 
finished with the Allience. (How ever long that takes)  I will not 
attack the Maximals untill the Allience is destroyed. But After that, 
they will join the ark, and become ancient history."

She walked back into the base. She was feeling very confident and 
starting to get her piorities straightened out.
